{"tid":2127232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金正恩：實施最大緊急體制  「脫北者回流播毒」朝認失守封開城","createTime":"2020-07-27T08:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T08:32:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b4fde5050663ce54e06ae7c8491f86b96c3c30ed","tid":2127232,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200727/CNFVSD3HTO7LZA5KMOUN6HMUII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200727%2FCNFVSD3HTO7LZA5KMOUN6HMUII%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=21c2b0f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200727%2FCNFVSD3HTO7LZA5KMOUN6HMUII%2F&h=8b881b07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200727/CNFVSD3HTO7LZA5KMOUN6HMUII/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n金正恩：實施最大緊急體制 <br />\n「脫北者回流播毒」朝認失守封開城<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n北韓首次承認被武漢肺炎的「惡毒病毒入侵」，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。分析認為北韓選擇承認被南韓「連累」，有利於向首爾施壓尋求援助。<br />\n<br />\n據朝中社昨天報道說，。。。。。。。。。。。。並且將實行約半年的「國家緊急防疫體系」升級為「最大緊急體制」。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，金正恩在政治局會議上宣告，「惡毒的病毒可以說已進入國家」，他並聲稱甫得知出現疑似個案後，就立即下令封鎖開城。北韓在今年1月底已經「鎖國」，但封城則是首次。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ISuyeHddjOPlwOLiPgv9HJzBT0k=/640x413/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C74DMRZSHX2QSTQXQWZBUNNSBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FISuyeHddjOPlwOLiPgv9HJzBT0k%3D%2F640x413%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC74DMRZSHX2QSTQXQWZBUNNSBA.jpg&h=685a43d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓宣佈緊急封鎖開城以防疫情擴散。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料早由走私客自華傳入<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：靠近分界線 兩韓經濟合作象徵<br />\n<br />\n朝中社指，疑似病例是一名三年前叛逃到南韓的脫北者，他上周日在位於兩韓邊境的開城市，從南韓一側非法偷渡返回北韓被截獲，經檢查發現疑似感染武漢肺炎病毒；防疫機關將他徹底隔離外，亦追蹤他入境後接觸過的人和其間到過開城的人，全部做了檢測和隔離。<br />\n<br />\n脫北者鮮有「回流」，不過南韓軍方昨天證實「高度可能」有一名脫北者近日已返回北韓。南韓多個傳媒和脫北者圈中人都指，有一名24歲脫北男性，因涉嫌強姦受查，日前已游水北逃回朝。<br />\n<br />\n據指政治局會議。。。。。。。。。。。。。已構成「危險情況&hellip;&hellip;可能引致致命的、毀滅性的災難」。<br />\n<br />\n外界一般不相信北韓無確診個案。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。其實是因為北韓近日接連舉行多場群眾大會，確診與疑似個案都增加，為阻疫情散播所以有此安排。<br />\n<br />\n北韓與中國邊界長達1,400公里，本就難以嚴封，冬天冰封鴨綠江時，更易出入，專家認為病毒很可能早就由走私客自中國帶入北韓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有利向首爾施壓求援<br />\n<br />\n峨山政策研究院分析員高明鉉（譯音）直言，「北。。。。。。。。。。。。：脫北者都是「危險人物」。南韓目前每日一般有數十個新增確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n南韓統一研究院高級院士趙韓範（譯音）亦指，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。韓援助」。上周朝中社報道指金正恩到工地視察，不滿進度，大發雷霆，下令撤換負責的官員。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社/美聯社"},{"pid":"43e19e5671f2377e1f93644b81198a466170278f","tid":2127232,"uid":195894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"脫北者會走返去北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170eee6d108fec8374d9dd617a733c5443d4b836","tid":2127232,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43e19e5671f2377e1f93644b81198a466170278f","tid":2127232,"uid":195894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"脫北者會走返去北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"明明係捉番去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c8d8f4d507b69598b953bd585741b974fbd53f","tid":2127232,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43e19e5671f2377e1f93644b81198a466170278f","tid":2127232,"uid":195894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"脫北者會走返去北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"係南韓衰性侵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1faa414a934a1f8fa587dfe28da952aa7ae75649","tid":2127232,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:24:54.000Z","msg":"死肥閪早西早著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcc2ce439552dcfcd60fc8b859d3b9188d535b3","tid":2127232,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9c8d8f4d507b69598b953bd585741b974fbd53f","tid":2127232,"uid":265192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"43e19e5671f2377e1f93644b81198a466170278f","tid":2127232,"uid":195894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"脫北者會走返去北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"係南韓衰性侵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"放出去間碟回流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b645e36c085a5ee6fe78ef6a782a8031af8121","tid":2127232,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"李屍朝鮮"}]}